			h2 Movement
			h3 General rules
			p Each square can only be occupied by one piece. A piece cannot capture another piece if it belongs to the same player. A piece cannot be placed outside of the board. A piece cannot jump over another piece except for the Horse. If a piece lands on a square occupied by the opponent's piece it can capture it by setting it on his sideboard. A captured piece can be placed back on the board. A piece captures in the direction of movement.
			h3 Pieces
			h4 Unpromoted pieces
